{"id":455849,"date":[{"year":1964,"month":6,"day":5}],"page":"4","source":"","region":"","masthead":"","special_issue":"笔会","column":"","genre":"","count":"221","ytitle":"","mtitle":"儿歌两首","ftitle":"","authors":["李尚元","刘饶民"],"text":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"妈妈"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"李尚元"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"妈妈穿上花衣裳，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"对着镜子忙梳妆，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我问妈妈有啥事?"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"妈妈光笑不答腔。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"妈妈光笑不答腔，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一个劲儿上礼堂，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"哦!原来公社演大戏，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"妈妈扮演李双双。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"小卫生兵"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"刘饶民"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"小扫帚，靠墙角，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"妹妹拿了把地扫，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"扫了门里扫门外，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"灰尘垃圾都扫掉!"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"小拖把，墙角站，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"弟弟拿了擦地板，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"擦了一遍擦两遍，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"擦得地板亮闪闪。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"扫的净，擦的光，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"两个又去抹门窗，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"抹了门窗抹桌子，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"插朵鲜花满家香。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"妈妈回来吃一惊，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“是谁收拾这么净?”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"弟弟妹妹门后笑，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“我们两个卫生兵!”"}]}